title: King's Game
description:
King's Game

Based on a bestseller by Niels Krause-Kjaer, an honest journalist gets enmeshed in a parliamentary election fraud. Winner of the 2005 Bodil Award for Best Film. Written and directed by Nikolaj Arcel and stars Anders W. Bertelsen, Soren Pilmark and Nastja Arcel. Written and directed by Nikolaj Arcel and stars Anders W. Bertelsen, Soren Pilmark and Nastja Arcel. 

From Denmark, in Danish
